snippet.title: SIEGE! Build and Defend - Reveal Trailer - Co-op Brawler Game
snippet.description:
UPDATE: "SIEGE!" got a new name. The game is now called "KnightOut". We are in the process of changing the name on all the platforms we use which may take some time. Sorry for the confusion.

Newsletter Sign up: http://siege.2ndstudio.com 

SIEGE! is a 2 - 4 player strategic brawler coming for PC on Steam this summer.

You start the game building your defences, and then you brawl it out in an epic battle with your friends till one of your kings die!
